  <header>
    <h1>Automotive Engineering Specialization</h1>
    <p>Master the fundamentals of automotive design, development, and manufacturing with comprehensive learning resources.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="specialization-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Specialization Areas</h2>
    <div class="specialization-grid">
  
      <!-- Powertrain Engineering -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-cogs"></i>
          Powertrain Engineering
        </div>
        <p>Focus on engine design, transmission systems, and alternative propulsion technologies.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Internal combustion engines</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Electric & hybrid powertrains</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Transmission systems</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title" style="font-size: larger; color: gold;">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/user/EngineeringExplained" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Engineering Explained</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/weberauto" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Weber Auto</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/technical-papers" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> SAE Technical Papers</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Vehicle Dynamics -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-car-side"></i>
          Vehicle Dynamics
        </div>
        <p>Study of vehicle motion, handling, stability, and control systems for optimal performance and safety.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Suspension systems</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Steering mechanisms</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Braking systems</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title" style="font-size: larger; color: gold;">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/@Learn-Engineering" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Learn Engineering</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCL6JmiMXKoXS6bpP1D3bk8g" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Donut Media</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.racecar-engineering.com/" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-globe"></i> Racecar Engineering</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Automotive Electronics -->
      <div class="specialization-card">
        <div class="specialization-title">
          <i class="fas fa-microchip"></i>
          Automotive Electronics
        </div>
        <p>Focus on electrical systems, control units, sensors, and advanced driver assistance systems.</p>
        <br>
        <ul class="features-list">
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> ECU programming</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Sensor integration</li><br>
          <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> ADAS development</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <div class="resources-section">
          <div class="resources-title" style="font-size: larger; color: gold;">Learning Resources</div><br>
          <ul class="channel-list">
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/Autotechlabs-Brand" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Auto Tech Labs</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.youtube.com/c/LearnEmbeddedSystems" target="_blank"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i> Learn Embedded Systems</a></li>
            <li><a style="color: white; text-decoration: none;" href="https://www.amazon.com/Automotive-Electronics-Handbook-Ronald-Jurgen/dp/0070344531" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Automotive Electronics Handbook</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
  
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <!-- Projects section -->
  <section class="projects-section">
    <h2 class="section-title">Industry Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-car-battery"></i>
          EV Battery Management
        </div>
        <p>Design and implement battery management systems for electric vehicles.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Thermal Management</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Cell Balancing</span>
          <span class="project-tag">BMS Architecture</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.mdpi.com/2313-0105/9/3/152" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Research</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
          Autonomous Vehicle Systems
        </div>
        <p>Develop perception, planning, and control systems for self-driving vehicles.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">Sensor Fusion</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Path Planning</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Computer Vision</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.udacity.com/course/self-driving-car-engineer-nanodegree--nd0013" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Course</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project-card">
        <div class="project-title">
          <i class="fas fa-wind"></i>
          Aerodynamic Optimization
        </div>
        <p>Improve vehicle performance through computational fluid dynamics and wind tunnel testing.</p>
        <div class="project-tags">
          <span class="project-tag">CFD Analysis</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Drag Reduction</span>
          <span class="project-tag">Downforce</span>
        </div>
        <a href="https://www.ansys.com/academic/educators/education-resources/aerodynamic-analysis-with-ansys-fluent-part-1" class="learn-btn" target="_blank">View Tools</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Core Concepts</h2>
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Vehicle Dynamics & Handling</div>
        <p>Understand the principles of vehicle motion, stability, and control.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-367/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Powertrain Systems</div>
        <p>Master the fundamentals of engines, transmissions, and drivetrain components.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/powertrain/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Automotive Materials</div>
        <p>Learn about materials selection, properties, and applications in vehicle design.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/standards/aerospace-material-specifications/385" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="topics-grid">
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Internal Combustion Engines</div>
        <p>Study engine design, thermodynamics, combustion processes, and performance optimization.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://saemobilus.sae.org/books/internal-combustion-engine-handbook-r-345" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Suspension & Steering Systems</div>
        <p>Understand suspension geometry, steering mechanisms, and their impact on vehicle handling.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://dl.ojocv.gov.et/admin_/book/Automotive%20Suspension%20%26%20Steering%20Systems%20%282%20Volumes%29%2C%204th%20Edition%20%28%20PDFDrive%20%29.pdf" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Braking Systems</div>
        <p>Learn about hydraulic, pneumatic, and regenerative braking technologies and safety systems.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-395/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Automotive Aerodynamics</div>
        <p>Study airflow around vehicles, drag reduction techniques, and performance optimization.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-348/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Electric & Hybrid Vehicles</div>
        <p>Explore electric motors, battery systems, power electronics, and hybrid architectures.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-561/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Vehicle Electronics & Control Systems</div>
        <p>Master automotive electrical systems, ECUs, sensors, and control algorithms.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-413/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">NVH (Noise, Vibration & Harshness)</div>
        <p>Learn techniques for analyzing and reducing noise and vibration in vehicles.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-481/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Vehicle Safety Engineering</div>
        <p>Study crash dynamics, occupant protection systems, and safety regulations.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-341/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Automotive Manufacturing</div>
        <p>Understand production processes, quality control, and assembly techniques.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.sae.org/publications/books/content/r-344/" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Autonomous Vehicle Technology</div>
        <p>Explore sensors, perception systems, decision-making algorithms, and control strategies.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://www.rand.org/content/dam/rand/pubs/research_reports/RR400/RR443-2/RAND_RR443-2.pdf" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Vehicle Thermal Management</div>
        <p>Study cooling systems, HVAC, and thermal optimization for conventional and electric vehicles.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://go.sae.org/mythermalinfo.html" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
  
      <div class="topic-card">
        <div class="topic-title">Automotive Lightweighting</div>
        <p>Learn strategies for weight reduction through material selection and structural optimization.</p>
        <a class="learn-btn" href="https://go.sae.org/lightweighting.html" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  

  <section class="practice-section">
